# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  methods  - get / set / report
#
#
# <Device>
#  Server to Gateway
#  - get.{devtype}.devinfo.{idx}
#  - get.{devtype}.state.{idx}
#  - get.{devtype}.config.{idx}
#
#  - set.{devtype}.state.{idx}
#  - set.{devtype}.config.{idx}
#
# Gateway to Server
#  - report.{devtype}.state.{idx}
#
# < Gateway>
#  Server to Gateway
#  - get.gateway.devlist
#  - get.gateway.devinfo
#  - set.gateway.upgrade
#
# Gateway to Server
#  - report.gateway.state
#  - get.time
#
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  유도등
#  -
